Install Linux Distribution
Install Ubuntu https://www.microsoft.com/en-in/p/ubuntu/9nblggh4msv6 from Microsoft Store.
Once the installation is complete, open "Ubuntu" from start-menu.
Enter a new username and password for the WSL environment when prompted.
Note
Password will not be visible when you're typing.
Common Errors

1. WslRegisterDistribution failed with error: 0x80080005
Error: 0x80080005 Server execution failed
Uninstall Ubuntu, follow the below steps, and reinstall ubuntu.

Please ensure that CPU virtualization and Virtual Machine Platform Windows features are enabled.

CPU Virtualization:

Open Task Manager.
Click on the performance tab, There you can see virtualization is enabled or not.
If it's not enabled please enable it in BIOS Settings.
Virtualization
For Virtual Machine Platform :

Search for Windows Features in your taskbar.
Then look for Virtual Machine Platform and enable it.
Virtual Machine Platform
